WEBVTT

00:02.540 --> 00:04.034
Happy Birthday, Dad!

00:04.058 --> 00:05.848
Aww. Thanks, guys.

00:07.558 --> 00:09.097
"Happy 80th Birthday."

00:09.098 --> 00:10.467
Anna-Kat, that's not my age.

00:10.468 --> 00:12.177
Seemed like a reasonable guess.

00:12.178 --> 00:13.807
And why is the tiger on the card
attacking me?

00:13.808 --> 00:14.967
So many notes.

00:14.968 --> 00:17.204
Do you want the card or not?

00:17.228 --> 00:19.267
And this is from me.

00:19.268 --> 00:22.387
99 shares of CincoNext.

00:22.388 --> 00:23.637
They're doing
some really incredible things

00:23.638 --> 00:24.927
in the biotech space.

