they could be worth millions.

00:27.928 --> 00:28.728
Or nothing.

00:28.729 --> 00:30.557
Or <i> millions.</i>

00:30.558 --> 00:31.767
Happy Birthday, Dad!

00:31.768 --> 00:33.177
Aww.

00:33.178 --> 00:34.677
It's a coupon for one clean room.

00:34.678 --> 00:36.057
Hm.

00:36.058 --> 00:38.227
I'm 9 years old. What's <i> your</i> excuse?

00:38.228 --> 00:41.267
What? Dad's always riding me
to clean my room, so now I will.

00:41.268 --> 00:43.735
Actually, I love it,
and I'm cashing it in now.

00:43.759 --> 00:44.767
Go clean your room.

00:44.768 --> 00:47.609
Damn. I was really banking
on you losing the coupon.

00:47.633 --> 00:50.542
Three kids with three gifts
all coming in under $1.

00:50.543 --> 00:52.809
So what? Where's <i> your</i> gift?

00:52.833 --> 00:55.172
- Mom forgot!
- No, I didn't!

00:55.173 --> 00:57.752
I would never, ever forget
my husband's birthday.

00:57.753 --> 00:59.274
<i>Okay, I did!</i>

00:59.298 --> 01:01.292
<i>Now lash out at the kids
to draw attention away from it.</i>

01:01.293 --> 01:02.672
It is your father's birthday,

01:02.673 --> 01:04.212
and you're not even
making him breakfast?!

01:04.212 --> 01:06.002
- All right! Okay.
- Okay.

01:06.003 --> 01:07.372
Who raised you?!

01:07.373 --> 01:08.833
Don't answer that!

01:10.793 --> 01:12.922
I have your present,
but I can't give it to you yet

01:12.923 --> 01:14.422
because it's a surprise.

01:14.423 --> 01:15.582
For <i> tonight.</i>

01:15.583 --> 01:16.832
- I knew it.
- Mm-hmm.

01:16.833 --> 01:18.602
You're throwing me
the birthday dinner party

01:18.626 --> 01:20.649
you've always promised me!

01:20.673 --> 01:23.872
Yeah, buddy! How'd you know?!

01:23.873 --> 01:25.422
Finally, an adult dinner party.

01:25.423 --> 01:27.082
- Nay... a salon,
- Mm.

01:27.083 --> 01:29.873
where we discuss art
and wear scarves indoors!

01:33.633 --> 01:36.091
I've been asking for years,
and now we're doing it!

01:36.673 --> 01:39.332
Now, only question left is...

01:39.333 --> 01:40.672
which scarf should I wear?

01:40.673 --> 01:42.212
<i>The real question is,</i>

01:42.213 --> 01:43.808
<i>which scarf should I hang myself with?</i>

