01:51.262 --> 01:53.011
I forgot Greg's birthday.

01:53.012 --> 01:54.851
Ohh! That's bad.

01:54.852 --> 01:56.051
I did the same thing to Celeste,

01:56.052 --> 01:57.891
and that pretty much led to our divorce.

01:57.892 --> 02:00.115
Well, that and all
the other women you slept with

02:00.139 --> 02:01.141
who weren't your wife.

02:01.142 --> 02:03.551
Hey, she knew I was an Aries
when she married me.

02:03.552 --> 02:04.971
Oh, my God, what a great defense.

02:04.972 --> 02:06.972
- Did you use that in court?
- I did.

02:06.973 --> 02:08.351
But the judge was a Capricorn, so...

02:08.352 --> 02:09.851
Oh, my gosh. I'm so sorry.

02:09.852 --> 02:11.221
No hablo cuckoo.

02:11.222 --> 02:13.221
So, what's happening with Greg?

02:13.222 --> 02:15.011
I lied to him about
forgetting his birthday,

02:15.012 --> 02:16.681
so now I have to throw him
a dinner party.

02:16.682 --> 02:17.682
Can you two make it?

02:17.683 --> 02:19.221
Ah! Richard and I will be there.

02:19.222 --> 02:21.416
Anything to get away from the kids.

02:21.440 --> 02:23.931
"Mom! Play board games with us!"

02:23.932 --> 02:25.719
I swear it's like
they don't even know me.

02:25.743 --> 02:26.750
I'm in, too.

02:26.774 --> 02:28.101
Mind if I bring my new girlfriend?

02:28.102 --> 02:30.051
Her name is Crissy, she's a therapist,

02:30.052 --> 02:31.812
and I honestly think
she could be the one.

02:35.052 --> 02:36.851
Are you on Tinder right now?

02:36.852 --> 02:38.051
Wh... I'm just browsing.

02:38.052 --> 02:39.431
Oh, God.

02:44.722 --> 02:46.811
Are you sure you didn't forget
Dad's birthday?

02:46.812 --> 02:48.471
'Cause this all seems very last-minute.

02:48.472 --> 02:50.311
