or talking about his commute,

04:13.202 --> 04:16.351
- and Doris hits on you the entire time.
- No, she doesn't.

04:16.351 --> 04:17.887
Why'd you have to go give me a hernia?

04:17.913 --> 04:18.930
I don't know!

04:18.932 --> 04:20.391
