like I have a hernia?

04:28.762 --> 04:29.762
This'll help.

04:30.972 --> 04:32.891
Hi!

04:32.892 --> 04:34.552
Happy birthday, Greg!

04:34.577 --> 04:36.192
- Hi, everyone!
- Happy birthday!

04:36.217 --> 04:37.601
Hi.

04:37.602 --> 04:39.435
- Have we been here long enough?
- Shut up!

04:39.460 --> 04:41.261
Welcome! Let me take your coats.

04:41.262 --> 04:43.311
- Oh! I'm so glad we could come.
- Thank you.

04:43.312 --> 04:44.642
Good.

04:45.993 --> 04:47.102
Hernia!

04:49.052 --> 04:50.351
I have a hernia.

04:50.352 --> 04:52.953
His nether regions
are still quite blown out.

04:52.978 --> 04:54.154
Mm.

04:54.682 --> 04:56.721
Okay, OCD girl, have at it.

04:56.722 --> 04:58.435
Halloween, Christmas...

04:58.472 --> 05:00.641
this.

05:00.642 --> 05:02.101
Can I borrow your phone charger?

05:02.102 --> 05:03.932
Sure, if you can find it.

05:09.852 --> 05:11.257
