05:11.282 --> 05:12.569
My bib jersey!

05:12.594 --> 05:13.999
I've been looking everywhere for that!

05:14.024 --> 05:15.991
- Your what?
- My bib jersey.

05:15.992 --> 05:17.821
Whenever I eat something greasy
in my room,

05:17.822 --> 05:19.726
I put on a jersey to protect my clothes.

05:19.751 --> 05:20.791
Genius, right?

05:21.912 --> 05:23.611
I fear for your future.

05:23.612 --> 05:24.991
Aah!

05:24.992 --> 05:26.741
I can't believe
I touched your bib jersey!

05:26.742 --> 05:29.201
And there's nothing clean enough
in here to wipe my hands on!

05:29.202 --> 05:31.127
Don't worry... it's covered
in so much old food,

05:31.152 --> 05:32.491
there's no way you touched fabric.

05:32.492 --> 05:34.502
You should be in prison.

05:34.527 --> 05:35.701
Uh, guys?

05:35.726 --> 05:37.841
