05:41.242 --> 05:43.020
Uh, Mom?

05:43.045 --> 05:44.840
Visible... blood!

05:44.865 --> 05:46.451
'Kay.

05:50.532 --> 05:52.872
So, Richard, how are things?

06:00.742 --> 06:04.072
So, Crissy, Angela tells me
that you are a therapist.

06:04.097 --> 06:05.119
How do you like it?

06:05.144 --> 06:06.353
I think the better question is,

06:06.354 --> 06:07.995
how do <i> you</i> like being a mother?

06:11.064 --> 06:13.104
So, Richard, whatcha typing?

06:15.224 --> 06:16.353
Nothing?

06:16.354 --> 06:18.313
All right.

06:18.314 --> 06:19.523
What are we going to do?

06:19.524 --> 06:21.853
Mom and Dad are going to kill us!

06:21.854 --> 06:23.490
Well, Dad's gonna lecture us,

06:23.515 --> 06:26.570
