07:02.184 --> 07:04.933
So, Greg, you seem to be
recovering nicely.

07:04.934 --> 07:06.143
Recovering?

07:06.144 --> 07:08.813
From the hernia surgery...

07:08.814 --> 07:10.183
that you had.

07:10.184 --> 07:11.853
Oh, yes. Well,
the procedure went smoothly.

07:11.878 --> 07:12.871
It was no big deal.

07:12.896 --> 07:15.009
Katie said it was a <i> very</i> big deal,
with a lot of complications.

07:16.854 --> 07:18.223
Oh... yeah.

07:18.224 --> 07:20.183
It going smoothly
actually <i> was</i> a complication

07:20.184 --> 07:21.933
because they expected it to be bad,

07:21.934 --> 07:23.723
but then when it looked
like it was good,

07:23.724 --> 07:25.183
it threw everyone off, and...

07:25.184 --> 07:27.789
because they were like,
"Aah! Why isn't this going bad?"

07:27.814 --> 07:29.183
And then, um...

07:29.184 --> 07:31.338
I started bleeding out of my... butt.

07:32.484 --> 07:33.684
I'll get that.

07:38.524 --> 07:39.644
Mmm.

07:41.389 --> 07:43.178
What?

07:43.179 --> 07:45.298
How are you carrying that
if you just had hernia surgery?

07:45.299 --> 07:47.008
Oh, these...

07:47.009 --> 07:49.758
darn pain meds give me
a false sense of strength.

07:49.759 --> 07:51.838
I hope I'm not bleeding
from my butt again.

07:51.839 --> 07:53.678
What's going on?!

07:53.679 --> 07:54.718
Okay.

07:54.719 --> 07:55.838
We lied.

07:55.839 --> 07:57.758
Greg didn't have hernia surgery.

07:57.759 --> 08:00.178
They're our friends.
We should tell them the truth.

08:00.179 --> 08:01.838
Yes, thank you.

08:01.839 --> 08:05.798
The real reason that we couldn't
go to dinner last week is...

08:07.469 --> 08:08.889
