for quite some time.

08:44.839 --> 08:47.468
I know... it's shocking.

08:47.469 --> 08:49.138
- Is it?
- Makes sense to me.

08:49.139 --> 08:51.428
Okay. Please take your seats for dinner.

08:51.429 --> 08:53.468
Katie, if I could talk to you
for a second?

08:53.469 --> 08:57.008
