about our terrible marriage.

08:59.639 --> 09:01.968
So,<i> that's</i> coming clean to
your friends? Just another lie?

09:01.969 --> 09:03.258
I had to!

09:03.259 --> 09:05.218
You couldn't fake a hernia,
so I had to pivot!

09:05.219 --> 09:06.638
Well, now everyone thinks
our marriage is in trouble.

09:06.639 --> 09:08.008
But it's not!

09:08.009 --> 09:09.758
You understand how lying works, right?

09:09.759 --> 09:11.258
But everyone bought it so easily.

09:11.259 --> 09:12.428
No one was like, "Whaaaat?!"

09:12.429 --> 09:13.798
