09:13.799 --> 09:15.928
Couples therapy is the perfect lie.

09:15.929 --> 09:18.928
It's personal, so no one will
ask any follow-up questions.

09:18.929 --> 09:20.008
I don't like it one bit.

09:20.009 --> 09:21.508
We won, Greg!

09:21.509 --> 09:23.429
Take the win! Enjoy it!

09:25.139 --> 09:28.218
And remember, we need to fake
like we're in a rough patch.

09:28.219 --> 09:30.598
