as you usually do.

09:30.599 --> 09:32.258
That won't be hard.

09:35.889 --> 09:38.008
Guys, I'm not trying to be cocky,

09:38.009 --> 09:39.468
but I think we did it.

09:39.469 --> 09:41.048
Yeah, great job, Taylor.

09:41.049 --> 09:42.508
But I also went
and got this from the attic

09:42.509 --> 09:43.798
so we can paint over it.

09:43.799 --> 09:46.388
Now we just need a screwdriver
to open the can.

09:46.389 --> 09:47.888
I'll just go downstairs and grab one.

09:47.889 --> 09:49.718
