09:49.719 --> 09:52.139
Trust me... she won't even notice.

09:54.599 --> 09:56.678
Visible blood!

09:56.679 --> 09:57.719
'Kay.

10:00.057 --> 10:01.572
Okay!

10:01.597 --> 10:02.961
Um, we're gonna
have to open the paint can

