is just preventative...

10:42.199 --> 10:43.598
like ant traps.

10:43.599 --> 10:45.869
That's a fun topic.
Let's talk about ants.

10:45.894 --> 10:48.338
Did you know they can lift
30 times their body weight?

10:48.339 --> 10:50.860
Greg, look, there's no shame
in therapy, okay?

10:50.885 --> 10:52.735
Some of the most prominent
people in Westport see me.

10:52.760 --> 10:54.888
I mean, should the Mayor
be ashamed of his sessions?

10:54.889 --> 10:57.534
Isn't that a breach
of client confidentiality?

10:59.009 --> 11:00.639
Shoot.

11:02.549 --> 11:04.468
Don't be hard on yourself, Greg.

11:04.469 --> 11:06.672
<i>Any</i> man would've been worn down by now.

11:06.697 --> 11:08.178
- We totally get it.
- Yeah.

11:08.179 --> 11:11.604
I'm sorry, but what exactly
do you totally get?

11:11.629 --> 11:13.541
