11:13.566 --> 11:14.627
that we're in therapy?

11:14.652 --> 11:16.098
- Katie!
- Katie!

11:16.099 --> 11:18.838
Greg, tell them that is <i> not</i> the case.

11:18.863 --> 11:21.178
- It's... the case.
- Mm.

11:21.179 --> 11:23.008
Can I talk to you in your office
for a second?

11:23.009 --> 11:25.546
