11:31.291 --> 11:33.290
but I love to watch him walk away.

11:34.371 --> 11:36.160
Mnh.

11:36.161 --> 11:37.392
"Poor Greg"?

11:37.417 --> 11:38.978
It should be "Poor Katie"!

11:39.003 --> 11:41.307
We won, Katie. Take the win.

11:41.332 --> 11:43.790
- Enjoy it!
- You like this.

11:43.791 --> 11:46.410
- This is a little victory for you.
- Mm-hmm.

11:46.411 --> 11:47.540
